<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; }
    .header { background: #007bff; color: #fff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; padding: 20px; }
    .highlight { color: #007bff; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Subscription Activated!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>Your <span class="highlight">NotifyX {{plan}}</span> subscription is now active!</p>
      <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> ₹{{amount}}</p>
        <p><strong>Valid Until:</strong> {{endDate}}</p>
      </div>
      <p>You can now access all the features included in your plan. Start exploring job opportunities that match your profile!</p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing NotifyX.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2026 X Careers Connect Private Limited. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
